description:
BEYOND the DARKNESS goes Darker today with The Horrific Haunting of Jeanine!

Dave & Tim visit with a woman with a tormented past and living a personal hell. Brain storms, Cult Activity and Violent Attacks continue to occur to Jeanine and her 5 children and she implores the Darkness Duo for help on today's show.
